BaBSay1.attackerAttack: This is MY city! YOU don't BELONG in it!

BaBSay2.attackerAttack: Whoever sent you WILL regret messing with the Back Alley Brawler!

BaBSay3.attackerAttack: I'm getting sick and tired of these aliens attacking MY home!

BaBSay4.attackerAttack: Stay frosty Psyche. We aren't leavin' until each of these things are wiped out!

Snap_Shot.help: A quick attack that fires an arrow at your foe after only minimal aiming. Fast, but little damage. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Fast

messages.attackerHit: You hit {PlayerDest} with your {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Lethal damage.
messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} hits you with their {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Lethal damage.

Call_Genin.help: Calls forth one to three Genin Ninja (depending on your level) to do your bidding. Genin have good reflexes and jumping skill, but they are still the lowest rank Ninja and only possess the most rudimentary skills, However, they can be trained in more advanced techniques and weapons. You may only have 3 Genin under your control at any given time. If you attempt to call Genin, you can only replace the ones you have lost in battle. If you already have three, the power will fail. Recharge: Very Long

PsycheSay1.attackerAttack: We'll send you back to where you belong!

PsycheSay2.attackerAttack: You all picked the wrong planet to mess with!

PsycheSay3.attackerAttack: You do not BELONG on our world! I'll be MORE than happy to escort you OFF of it!

PsycheSay4.attackerAttack: Don't worry Brawler. I'm here with you until this is finished!

Plasma_Blast.help: Plasma burns are hard to heal. The burns have halted your Regeneration rate.
